Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全身都是泡泡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}頭髮變得好毛躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小萬里 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像快沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…不會吧
Comment: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:34.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:50.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:54.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:01:00.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ひとすじの光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:04.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:09.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:14.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷い　歩く術を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:22.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:24.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:30.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:35.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:40.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今もかすかな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:45.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:50.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:58.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう未来と過去が交差する　百年目の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:50.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一切都始於這靜靜燃燒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:54.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在長夜將明之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:01:00.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一道光芒 一聲發自靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:04.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}衝破束縛 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:09.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}尋求著歸宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:14.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷茫地邁足前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:22.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}這顆被波濤掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:24.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}甚至沒辦法保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:30.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 就像要跳出來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:35.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}留下無法忘卻的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:40.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}希望這微弱的殘影 永遠不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:45.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界正在等待 屬於明日的嬰啼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:50.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 千萬不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:58.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}是的 這是一首交錯著過去與未來的百年長歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,10,,{\blur5}標記的位置就是目擊過武藏號的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,10,,{\blur5}她們是打算去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得她們是想靠近本土吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校是說叫我們去追武藏號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目前通訊無礙 而且能接受調遣的好像只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許就像美波同學說得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家是不是都被那個像老鼠一樣的東西弄得不正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們現在也只能在這片海域展開搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無法確認故障原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水箱應該已經修過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概有什麼地方還在漏水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能請求補給了 艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五天後才能和補給艦會合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前只能節約用水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸 你能去看看氣象圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}渴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就喝彈珠汽水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喝膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會喝胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn華康鋼筆體W2\bord0\1c&H59585B&\frz12.33\move(200,232,200,-200,0,2708)}水\N可\N是\N很\N珍\N貴\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.45,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fn華康鋼筆體W2\bord0\1c&H59585B&\frz11.31\move(630,746,620,226,0,3261)}各位同學請節約用水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼菜不用水就能做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想上廁所該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會吧 難道不准上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}廁所沖水是用海水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買了那麼多廁紙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是誰放鹽水的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.92,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我出來 到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你聽說小黑那件事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康鋼筆體W2\bord0.2\1c&H3B3B3B&\frz1.193\move(442,118,444,196,38,1998)}今\N天\N開\N始\N淋\N浴\N與\N泡\N澡\N將\N使\N用\N海\N水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三天沒洗了 洗還是不洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們的頭髮怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像爆炸頭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}頭髮可是女孩子的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水煮鯖魚 水煮番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什錦蔬菜 口糧餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一堆罐裝食品 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別那麼挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唉 沒辦法 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是下場雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我快到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不想讓內褲沾上海水的鹹味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有點噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不喜歡喝碳酸飲料嗎 小…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 那個 前方有霧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小聰 打開探照燈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸 鳴霧笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣根本沒辦法收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好不容易才接到一點雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是個大型低氣壓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 借一步說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.59,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暴雨天氣 禁止前往上層甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.93,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重複一遍 禁止前往上層甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能走甲板還真是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.93,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4}然後呀 她的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.71,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur4}今天的晚餐是什麼呢 我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}岬同學 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去找個人代班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天啊 帥爆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.25,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你對我家真知知做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.24,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你叫我怎麼冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.33,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要制裁她 你給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要拿下你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「跟拔蛀牙一樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「輕而易舉」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這句真是經典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常之贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要在我房間看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我房間沒電視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長你也要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是這一段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 很抱歉這麼晚還來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 能代我班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「怎麼了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「張嘴說話啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}外面聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「張嘴說話啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「是嗎 沒辦法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「咱去一趟了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「豈能輕易拜了一下風」 嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這麼怕打雷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷公又不會偷走肚臍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.61,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※日本傳說雷公會偷走小孩的肚臍。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是怕打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會想起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位乘客 本船已發送求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在藍色人魚趕來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請保持冷靜 聽從救援人員的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.03,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}水漲上來了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.60,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明乃 快點跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽呢 他們怎麼不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我能早點跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸媽媽或許就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 有求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰發出的求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新橋商店街船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全長135公尺 總噸位14000
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷傾側 好像是進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乘員有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總乘員552名 現在正在避難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}附近還有船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是距離最近的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聯絡藍人總部和學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是航海艦晴風號艦長 岬明乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是新橋 在法拉洛普島東南13海浬處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}15分鐘前 在航行時撞上了暗礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目前船體中央依然掛在暗礁上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十人輕傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進水了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷應該是進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起火了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了 我艦大約50分鐘後可以抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前請船長您繼續引導避難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鈴 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全體聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烏利西環礁附近有船隻觸礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本艦將前往營救此船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備海難救援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮雷科及航海科的非執勤人員請立即開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟啦糟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚇死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天氣晴朗 不過風大浪高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風暴過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}低氣壓往西邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傾斜角度約為40度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超過50度時很可能就會傾覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是新橋的船內地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前三層都是商店 四層是居住分區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中央是艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好救援準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也開跳艇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這個艦長又打算擅離職守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為艦長 這種時候該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有點不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長就待在船上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰去指揮救援隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那我在船上指揮你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 明娜 加上炮雷科的三個人登船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潛水隊入海確認船體受損情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海科與急救員引導登上救生艇的人去晴風號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國中時就接受過無數次救援訓練了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過實際操作還是頭一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總是不走運 不會出問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請看場合說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}點亮探照燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們已經抵達現場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甲板上都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甲板交給急救員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去搜救船內的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救援的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先應該清點人數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辨識手環呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該先清點傷患吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是帶指導手冊來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是晴風號副艦長宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在開始搜救船內倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居住分區好像還有人 麻煩各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灑水器沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}緊急系統被撞壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這艘船…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船體四號分區前約有120公尺長的裂紋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前面的三個分區好像已經進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是宗谷 新橋的緊急系統故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}立刻與新橋接舷 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}注意避開環礁 立刻把船上的人引導到甲板上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避難引導馬上就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多聞丸不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回過神時就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還很小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒搜查的只有五號分區飲食街了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去找多聞丸 你們先去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避難引導順利結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進去的救援隊也都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是副艦長和明娜同學好像還在船尾方面繼續搜救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像有個小孩不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我找這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫找那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多聞丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是指小貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 新橋要沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}解開稱人結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}徹底斷兩半了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 副艦長和明娜同學好像還在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事情大條了 事情大條了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小娜 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明娜 跑快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫不是正在跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們減速 你跳下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 副艦長 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船體中央裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去船會沉的 快點出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們接回了明娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聯繫不上她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也很怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我總是不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能坐著等死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等待原來這麼痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經和小白說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發毛毯給避難人員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外準備一些吃的 還有熱飲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都還在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海科的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和避難人員一起回晴風號了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只剩副艦長一個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是藍色人魚緊急響應艦隊的岸間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是晴風號炮雷科的小笠原光救援隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦各位了 剩下的交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船上還有一個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救援對象 一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避難人員都有吃飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有傷員的話報告給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要吃粥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有年糕紅豆湯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是這麼不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有探測到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我錘子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 救援艦說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍色人魚目前正在搜救副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現救援對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}周邊一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}千萬別亂動 我們馬上進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}活著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們得救了喵 真是太好了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要學貓叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功救出多聞丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多聞丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多聞丸 你該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牠很喜歡你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 多聞丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能請你照顧牠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩各位了 請把牠轉交橫須賀女子海洋學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抗體及其個人使用報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等你的期間一直很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還以為會把你永遠留在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船上能不能再擠一隻？艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}專業藍人不愧是專業的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前我遇難的時候也被她們救過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才想成為藍色人魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且我覺得上了船以後 或許就能有家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我媽媽以前是藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她說 海上的夥伴們就像一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我和明明成為藍色人魚之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定能得到一個大家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我們做個約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你才總是說 海上的夥伴們都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個叫萌香的就是武藏號的艦長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫和我們艦長西婭 也是國中以來的老交情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}病毒的抗體已經做好了 好想快點去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:24.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,488)}多災多難的暴雨之夜！
Comment: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:25.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ED-FF
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:37.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:43.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:07.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:13.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:21.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:30.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:34.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:38.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:44.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:53.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:37.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我會比話語還要溫柔 輕輕地推著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:43.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是啊 這就是你和我之間的漣漪效應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}面前的驚濤駭浪 一浪捲來一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:07.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}我們選擇的航路 就是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:13.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}如果你忘記了微笑 我會笑給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:21.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}流過眼淚之後 讓堅強隨波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:30.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:34.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}比話語還要溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:38.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}是這片晴空和習習涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:44.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描繪夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}我希望我就是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:53.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}要相信春天正在等待著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:24:00.07,End,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&H59CAEF&,&HC4FFFD&,&H59CAEF&,&HC4FFFD&)\pos(922,416)}下\N集\N也\N請\N找\N個\N
